            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> any<br/><b>Organization</b> solitary or pair<br/><b>Treasure</b> NPC Gear (masterwork dagger, <i>cloak of resistance +1</i>, skull, spell component pouch, spellbook, 348 gp)"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Skeletal mages are minor spellcasters (typically 5th-level or less) who have retained both their intelligence and their spellcasting abilities. These variant skeletal champions gain Silent Spell as a bonus feat. Like skeletal champions, skeletal mages cannot be created with <i>animate dead</i>\u2014they only arise under rare conditions or through ancient, esoteric rituals."
        }
